  <diagram name="Страница-1" id="GsL5VCL8RDukLzRFZ04q">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1664" dy="2093" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\nskinparam maxMessageSize 150\nautonumber\n\nactor User\nparticipant \&quot;AppleWatch\&quot; as watch\nparticipant \&quot;Game\&quot; as game\nparticipant \&quot;Workout\&quot; as workout\nparticipant \&quot;Character\&quot; as character\nparticipant \&quot;Resource\&quot; as resource\nparticipant \&quot;Achievement\&quot; as achievement\nparticipant \&quot;NotificationService\&quot; as notifier\n\nUser -&gt; watch: Initiate data sync\nactivate watch\n\nwatch -&gt; watch: syncData()\n\nloop For each unsynced workout record\n    watch -&gt; game: addWorkoutData(duration, calories)\n    activate game\n\n    &#39; Створення об&#39;єкта тренування\n    create workout\n    game -&gt; workout: &lt;&lt;create&gt;&gt; Workout(date, duration, calories)\n    activate workout\n    workout --&gt; game: workout created\n    deactivate workout\n\n    &#39; FR-09: Логіка щоденних квестів\n    note over game: Check Daily Quest: Burn 300 kcal\n    alt Calories burned &gt;= 300\n        game -&gt; resource: add(bonusPoints)\n        activate resource\n        resource --&gt; game: points added\n        deactivate resource\n        \n        game -&gt; achievement: unlock()\n        activate achievement\n        achievement --&gt; game: achievement unlocked\n        deactivate achievement\n\n        game -&gt; notifier: sendNotification(\&quot;Daily Quest Complete! Bonus added.\&quot;)\n        activate notifier\n        notifier --&gt; game: ok\n        deactivate notifier\n    end\n\n    &#39; Оновлення персонажа (XP та Level)\n    game -&gt; character: upgrade()\n    activate character\n    character --&gt; game: status updated\n    deactivate character\n\n    game --&gt; watch: workout processed\n    deactivate game\nend\n\n&#39; FR-10: Друзі та Рейтинг (Leaderboard)\nUser -&gt; watch: Open Leaderboard\nactivate watch\nwatch -&gt; game: getWeeklyLeaderboard()\nactivate game\nnote right of game: Comparing progress among friends\ngame --&gt; watch: leaderboard data (ranks, xp)\ndeactivate game\n\nwatch --&gt; User: Display updated Character &amp; Rank\ndeactivate watch\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="TbrPXkx1jhJTEy8uwOdt-4">
